Package org.moeaframework.util.tree

Class Ceil

java.lang.Object
org.moeaframework.util.tree.Node
org.moeaframework.util.tree.Ceil
public class Ceil extends Node
The node for calculating the smallest integer value that is greater than or equal to a number. The inputs and outputs to this node are shown below:
Name Type Description
Argument 1 Number The number
Return Value Number The ceiling of the number
See Also:
